type: 1 * 3 ≡ fst (1, 3) * snd (1, 3) : int, value: true


class proj.errors.TypeCheckError: terms 1 * 3 and fst (1, 3) + snd (1, 3) are not definitionally equal


type: 1 < 3 ≡ fst (1, 3) < snd (1, 3) : bool, value: true


